# VisionGuard Safety AI

**Real-Time Computer Vision Platform for Workplace Safety, PPE Compliance, and Hazard Intelligence**

> 🚧 **Status: Phase 1 (Core MVP) — in active development.** This README grows with the project.

VisionGuard turns ordinary CCTV and video streams into a real-time safety monitoring system for construction sites, factories, warehouses, and labs. Instead of simply detecting objects, it reasons about the scene — continuously answering one operational question: **"Is this workplace safe right now?"**

---

## Planned Capabilities

| Phase | Features |
|-------|----------|
| **1 — Core MVP** | Multi-class detection (workers, PPE, vehicles) · multi-object tracking · PPE compliance engine · restricted-zone intrusion detection · fall detection · safety dashboard · PDF incident reports |
| **2 — Depth** | Calibrated worker–vehicle proximity (real-world meters via homography) · 0–100 Safety Risk Score · RAG-based AI safety assistant |
| **3 — Standout engineering** | Cross-camera Re-ID · ONNX/TensorRT edge optimization with measured benchmarks · temporal behavior model |

## Roadmap — Phase 1

